  ('dietitian-moex-11298', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於糖尿病的急性併發症DKA的敘述，何者正確？ 病人體內有足夠的insulin量  血糖通常會高至1000 mg/dL以上 病人會有寡尿的現象發生   病人通常會有換氣過度的情形發生', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "85ba92118f33", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "112", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11299', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '糖尿病人血糖之控制要達到何目標，以防止慢性併發症之發生？ 空腹血糖維持在80-120 mg/dL  空腹血糖維持在100-140 mg/dL HbA 維持在＜8％    飯後兩小時維持在＜200 mg/dL lc', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "85ba92118f33", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "112", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11300', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關糖尿病腎病變之敘述，何者正確？ 若無適當介入，則約有80％ type 2 DM會產生蛋白尿及高血壓 ACE inhibitors可降低蛋白尿及減緩糖尿病的腎病變 蛋白質予以1.5 g/kg/day可彌補尿蛋白之損失，並延緩GFR的下降 具有高血壓的糖尿病腎病變，其鈉量不必限制', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "85ba92118f33", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "112", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11301', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '糖尿病患者於清晨四點至八點時，會有血糖升高之情況，此稱為： morning syndrome    dawn phenomenon honeymoon effect    rebound effect', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "85ba92118f33", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "112", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 35, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11302', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列對癌症治療的敘述，何者最正確？ 放射線治療可破壞全身的癌細胞 化學治療易破壞小腸上皮層而引起腸炎 對鼻咽癌的治療而言，外科手術是優先選擇 許多癌症必須結合手術、放射及化療來共同治療', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "85ba92118f33", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "112", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-11303', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-2755cf97', 'sub-dietitian-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關痛風患者營養照顧之敘述，何者錯誤？ 急性發病期需嚴格限制飲食中嘌呤（purine）含量 飲用大量水分 控制蛋白質的量在1公克/公斤體重 快速減肥有助於痛風的改善', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "85ba92118f33", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "112", "s": "3001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "膳食療養學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 37, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL)
